---
title: Southern Cheesy Pork Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa
description: Juicy Southern-spiced pork, charred corn, sour cream and melted Cheddar cheese; it’s hard to resist these incredibly delicious quesadillas. Plus, it takes less than 30 minutes to have this fun feast on your dinner table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-southern-cheesy-pork-quesadillas-6b34ec6f.jpg
